<h2 style="text-align: center;">Implementation & Testing Progress Report 2 (Week 12)</h2>

<p><strong>Course:</strong> CSAI 499 – Senior Project<br>
<strong>Deliverable:</strong> Implementation & Testing Progress Report 2<br>
<strong>Team Number:</strong> 14<br>
